block main
  +section
    h2 A Static Site Generator & Web Development Framework
    p.lead Mimogear was built from the ground up to serve as a skeleton framework for html/pug, css/postcss, and javascript. By integrating gulp, a popular task runner, #[strong Mimogear will automatically compile, distribute, and watch development assets]. I hope you enjoy how easy it is to build as much as I enjoyed creating it!
    h4 Give Mimogear a try with a few setup commands in your terminal:
    code
      | $ git #[em clone] https://github.com/mimoduo/Mimogear.git#[br]
      | $ #[em cd] Mimogear#[br]
      | $ npm install#[br]
      | $ npm install gulp-cli -g#[br]
      | $ gulp
